data.value: ◾Download file below and extract Run Doppler Injector v0.1.exe Type in a process name into the box. Add the DLLs you want by clicking on the Add DLL button. You can also drag and drop them into the DLL list. Go into Settings and customise the settings to your liking. Everything should be straight forward. Click Inject and enjoy!
